summary: peter parker breaking down in tears when he comes to the newly renovated avengers compound made to look as homey as possible...
body:
peter parker breaking down in tears when he comes to the newly renovated avengers compound made to look as homey as possible with spruce wood floor with a smooth finish and when tony asks him whats wrong he wails “im too sticky to slide across this floor”

tony says hes being ridiculous but still starts wearing those kid socks with a bunch of little anti-sliding paws on the bottom in solidarity

harley, on the other hand, slides into the workshop doorframe the next day risky business style jamming out to ‘old time rock n roll’ and peter exclusively uses walls and the ceiling to go places ever since

summary: You know, I always recognized the general animal theme naming for Spider-Man villains (Dr. Octopus, Lizard, Rhino, Scorpion,...
body:
You know, I always recognized the general animal theme naming for Spider-Man villains (Dr. Octopus, Lizard, Rhino, Scorpion, Beetle, Chameleon, Vulture, Hammerhead, Razorback, Etc.) and the “elemental thugs” (Shocker, Electro, Sandman and his water palette-swap Hydro-Man), but it wasn’t until this PS4 game that I finally caught on to the generic Halloween theme as well- spider, (hob)goblin, Black Cat, Wolf-Man, Tombstone, Grim Reaper, Morbius the Living Vampire…

Mysterio’s kind of a magician/walking haunted house/horror show host, but that’s a bit of a stretch.
